{"tid":334771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"63歲「鳩摩智」為15歲女兒慶生 親嘴照引爭議","createTime":"2017-07-25T04:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T09:44:54.000Z","uid":72009,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aaafd3e1082195786485f5402c0404192aca1067","tid":334771,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:40:44.000Z","msg":"李國麟曬出和女兒親嘴的照片，有網友覺得不妥：「親臉會更好&hellip;&hellip;」「這有點過了，好像&hellip;&hellip;」「不是一般都親臉蛋的嗎？」但也有網友留言：「我支持你李老師，我和我家寶貝女兒也親，我老公也親，這是親情和愛，有些人就是矯情，自己私生活亂的一塌糊塗，人家親親自己孩子，單純的親情卻要被褻瀆！不理他們！」「父女感情真好，都說女兒就是爸爸上輩子的情人~」「齷齪的人看什麼都齷齪。」<br />\n<br />\n面對網友的議論，李國麟女兒李沅薐也在微博發聲：「很失望，真的很失望。本想與大家分享這美妙的一刻，只是純粹的與大家分享，沒有奢求過大家的祝福，但也沒想過會引來這麼多的唾罵。女兒親爸爸，一個傳達愛意的舉動，在我眼裡，我看見滿屏都是父愛，在你們眼裡卻想到亂倫。一個發自親情的吻卻被人們說得如此低俗，我真的感到很可笑。」圖為李沅薐慶生照。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/entertainment/jzb2jql.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fentertainment%2Fjzb2jql.html&d=CtS3Nn%2BaoEd%2BECsNizbbEnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3b85d753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/entertainment/jzb2jql.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/2ee7000330e51070d21f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F2ee7000330e51070d21f&h=31ab2241&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/31c000011530c0863c1e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F31c000011530c0863c1e&h=f1a842f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a8456bb7ee9a626f39f702e22330b6061c7a76","tid":334771,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"大奸角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f086fba2af0701faa4b4c1e91ea467de5d2a567","tid":334771,"uid":30678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"鬼父"},{"pid":"8cef8